        "\n",
        "$$\n",
        "\\textbf{Input: } x \\in \\mathbb{R} \\longrightarrow \\textbf{Output: } y \\in [0,1]\n",
        "$$\n",
        "\n",
        "## Sigmoid function\n",
        "\n",
        "The **sigmoid** (or **logistic**) function is exactly such a function.\n",
